        "commit",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画。标题设为「Merge feature to advanced main (Logistics_StockLevel)」。结构如下：先commit初始化，然后branch newbranch，checkout过去再commit，接着checkout回main做另一个commit，最后merge newbranch。",
