    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，是newbranch合并到main，箭头方向正确。标题已经包含「advanced main」和「Logistics_StockLevel」。我检查一下：merge newbranch这步是在checkout main之后执行的，所以目标分支确实是main。",
      "elements_involved": [
